  "title": "MERCHANDISING EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job\nSummary: </strong></u></p><p>The\nMerchandising Executive, you will play a pivotal role on product creation and after sales shoes’ handling process. You will\nwork with various departments, including the marketing, retail and accounts to\nensure smooth flow of work process. This\nposition requires strong attention to detail and the\nability to thrive in a fast-paced environment.</p><p><u><strong>Key\nResponsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Liaise with factories on product price\n     list and other relevant matters</li><li>Prepare Specification Sheet (in Chinese) for\n     each product </li><li>Creation of product detail in system</li><li>Prepare and upload franchise catalogue in\n     system</li><li>Handle shoes defect and minor repair</li><li>Assist the Merchandising Team in any\n     other matters</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Candidate\n     must possess at least a diploma in relevant fields</li><li>Minimum\n     3 Years of relevant working experience required  </li><li>Must be\n     able to speak and write both in English and Chinese\n     languages. This position needs <strong>to liaise with Chinese speaking\n     associates </strong></li><li>Meticulous, hardworking\n     and\n     responsible with a pleasant personality </li><li>Love\n     fashion, sense of adventure, and a strong team player</li></ul><p>If you are a creative, innovative and motivated individual\nlooking to join a dynamic and growing brand, we would love to hear from you! At\nprettyFIT, we believe in creating a positive and supportive work environment\nthat encourages growth and development. We offer competitive remuneration and\nbenefits packages, as well as opportunities for career advancement. To apply,\nplease submit your resume and cover letter to <a href=\"mailto:hr@prettyfit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hr@prettyfit.com.sg</a></p>",
